---
title: Sesame Szechuan Pork Noodles with Rainbow Cabbage & Peanuts
description: Sometimes, a sauce just steals the show. Case in point? This version, which combines zingy, spicy, aromatic Szechuan paste with nutty sesame oil, tangy rice wine vinegar, and a pinch of sugar. Totally mouthwatering and packed with umami flavor, it pairs perfectly with a tangle of chewy ramen noodles, and tender shredded cabbage. Each bowl is garnished with scallion green for brightness and chopped peanuts for satisfying crunch.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sesame-szechuan-pork-noodles-c7890158.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/sesame-szechuan-pork-noodles-5f061b065e92006b2f2ae5a0-ec31a474.pdf
