  carbohydrates: 90 g
  sugar: 15 g
  protein: 36 g
  fiber: 7 g
  sodium: 2420 mg
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
course: main course
time required: 25 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/sesame-szechuan-pork-noodles-5f061b065e92006b2f2ae5a0
cuisine: Chinese
